column5: LOL....I think it's fake...but it looks pretty cool.  Would I want it at the end of my line?  NOT ON YOUR LIFE!!!! haha...unless I was using 1000 lb test line or something...it would probably still pull my arms off though.
Well i have the equipment to catch him.  ...so where was that again i will leave right now...lol..lol... nice fake,but hey it was cool to watch      cheers
i cant believe people on youtube think thats real..........  ANYTHING is possible now-a-days with all the technology.....  hell, photoshop can even make Rosie O'Donnell look skinny.
hell, photoshop can even make Rosie O'Donnell look skinny.   i will believe that when i see it.  cheers!
hahahahahaha  Just an example of how powerful photoshop is....  Make me pretty!
This is more along the Rosie topic......
What makes you think that the Dove commercial is photoshop?????  Perhaps toning things down a little may avoid you being slammed by the lovely ladies that we have on this board!!!!

I am not talking about the lovely ladies on this site. I am saying that anything is possible with today's technology. And as a matter of fact, that dove commercial IS photoshop. But again, that has nothing to do with anyone on this site. My comment was about the technology.
